✅ Do’s
- Keep your profiles professional and respectful.
- Use strong privacy settings to control who sees your content.
- Share academic achievements, projects, or positive updates.
- Think before posting — consider how it reflects on you.
- Credit sources properly when sharing articles, images, or ideas.
❌ Don’ts
- Don’t post offensive or discriminatory comments.
- Don’t overshare personal information (address, phone number, etc.).
- Don’t engage in online arguments or trolling.
- Don’t use slang or casual language in professional groups.
- Don’t spread unverified news or misinformation.
